    "description": "The Herman Miller Aeron Size C is a large-format ergonomic office chair with Pellicle mesh, PostureFit SL lumbar support, and a 350 lb weight capacity, designed for users 6'0\"–6'6\".",
    "brand": { "@type": "Brand", "name": "Herman Miller" },
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "price": "1795.00",
      "priceCurrency": "USD",
      "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
            "priceValidUntil": "2027-03-01",
      "hasMerchantReturnPolicy": {
        "@type": "MerchantReturnPolicy",
        "applicableCountry": "US",
        "returnPolicyCategory": "https://schema.org/MerchantReturnFiniteReturnWindow",
        "merchantReturnDays": 30,
        "returnMethod": "https://schema.org/ReturnByMail",
        "returnFees": "https://schema.org/FreeReturn"
      },
      "shippingDetails": {
        "@type": "OfferShippingDetails",
        "shippingRate": {
          "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
          "value": "0",
          "currency": "USD"
        },
        "shippingDestination": {
          "@type": "DefinedRegion",
          "addressCountry": "US"
        },
        "deliveryTime": {
          "@type": "ShippingDeliveryTime",
          "handlingTime": {
            "@type": "QuantitativeValue",
            "minValue": 0,
            "maxValue": 1,
            "unitCode": "DAY"
          },
          "transitTime": {
            "@type": "QuantitativeValue",
            "minValue": 2,
            "maxValue": 7,
            "unitCode": "DAY"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What size is the Herman Miller Aeron for tall people?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Tall users 6'0\" and above should choose the Aeron Size C — the largest variant. The Size C has a seat height range of 16\"–20.5\", a fixed seat depth of approximately 18.5\", and a back height of ~23.5\". It is designed for users 6'0\"–6'6\" with lean to average builds. Users above 6'4\" with longer femurs may find the fixed seat depth limiting and should evaluate the Steelcase Leap Plus instead."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the seat height range of the Herman Miller Aeron Size C?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The Herman Miller Aeron Size C has a seat height range of 16 to 20.5 inches. For tall users, the key target is your popliteal height — the floor-to-knee-crease measurement. Most users 6'0\"–6'3\" fall within this range comfortably. Users 6'4\"+ may be near the top of the range; the Steelcase Leap Plus reaches 22.5\" for users who need more seat height."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is the Aeron Size C good for tall users with longer thighs?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The Aeron Size C's fixed 18.5\" seat depth works well for tall users whose thigh length falls within that measurement — typically those in the 6'0\"–6'3\" range with average proportions. If your thigh length is longer (common above 6'3\"), the fixed depth may not provide adequate thigh support without seat-edge pressure behind the knee. The Steelcase Gesture (adjustable to 18.75\") or Leap Plus (adjustable to 19.75\") offer more flexibility."
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
