        <a href="/chairs/herman-miller-aeron/seat-height/" class="block p-5 rounded-lg bg-card border border-border hover:bg-accent transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-heading mb-1 text-base">Seat Height Range</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">16"–20.5" range explained. Recommended settings by height for tall users 6'0"–6'5".</p>
